      <title>德国保守党候选人考虑削减 1000 亿欧元支出</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/germany-election-parties-gird-for-trump-economic-slump-in-campaign-push</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国保守党总理候选人在二月份大选前的民意调查中领先，他提议削减 1000 亿欧元（1050 亿美元）的移民和社会支出，以修复该国的财政状况。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/germany-election-parties-gird-for-trump-economic-slump-in-campaign-push</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Dec 2024 12:26:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列看到加沙停火谈判取得突破的迹象</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/israel-sees-signs-of-breakthrough-in-talks-over-gaza-ceasefire</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列官员表示，加沙停火的前景比过去一年中的任何时候都更加现实，这意味着期待已久的释放人质和增加对受困地区的援助的协议可能即将达成。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/israel-sees-signs-of-breakthrough-in-talks-over-gaza-ceasefire</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Dec 2024 11:43:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>消息人士称，莫斯科爆炸案中俄罗斯将军遇害</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/high-ranking-russian-general-killed-in-explosion-in-moscow</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位知情人士透露，周二凌晨，俄罗斯莫斯科发生爆炸，暗杀俄罗斯放射、化学和生物防御部队负责人，幕后黑手是乌克兰。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/high-ranking-russian-general-killed-in-explosion-in-moscow</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Dec 2024 06:28:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国政府被指控违反法律，未经处理的污水泄漏</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/uk-government-accused-of-breaking-law-by-allowing-sewage-spills</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一家公共监督机构周二表示，英国政府和监管机构允许水务公司在没有下雨的情况下将未经处理的污水排入支流，违反了法律，并威胁要采取法律行动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/uk-government-accused-of-breaking-law-by-allowing-sewage-spills</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Dec 2024 00:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普的豁免权主张未能结束纽约封口费案</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/trump-loses-bid-to-have-hush-money-case-tossed-over-immunity</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普未能说服法官以总统豁免权为由撤销对其在纽约封口费案中的定罪，但由于这位当选总统继续对判决提出其他质疑，该案件远未结束。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/trump-loses-bid-to-have-hush-money-case-tossed-over-immunity</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Dec 2024 23:44:48 GMT</pubDate>
